title: What are patients' overall experiences of out-of hours GP services?
analysis_commentary: The majority of patients are also happy with their overall experiences of out-of-hours GP services, but to a lesser extent than their overall experience of GP surgeries. Of the patients who responded in 2014/2015, 69% said their experiences of out-of-hours GP services were very and fairly good. This is an improvement on 2013/14 but lower than precentage recorded in 2011/12 and 2012/13.
